	Ear drops are medications in liquid form that are specifically designed to be applied directly into the ear canal.
	Hearing loss, ear fullness, tinnitus (ringing in the ears), earache, pressure.
	Some common eardrops used for various ear conditions are Antibiotic eardrops, Steroid eardrops, Earwax removal eardrops, Analgesic eardrops,
	Antifungal eardrops.
