	<h3><b>Eye Drops</b></h3>
	Eye drops are used to treat various eye conditions and symptoms. 
	Dryness, burning, itching, redness, foreign body sensation, tearing, swollen eyelids, pain, blurred vision.
	Some common eyedrops are Artificial tears, Antihistamine eye drops, Decongestant eye drops, Antibiotic eye drops, Steroid eye drops.
