	<h3><b>Headache</b></h3>
	A headache is a common condition characterized by pain or discomfort in the head or neck region.
	Some common symptoms of headaches include Pain or aching in the head or neck, pressure or tightness sensation, throbbing or pulsating pain,
	sensitivity to light or sound, nausea or vomiting, dizziness. Some tablets for headache are Tylenol, Advil, Aleve, Excedrin, Motrin, Bayer, Anacin,
	Aspirin, Saridon.

	<br />
	<a href="https://my.clevelandclinic.org/health/diseases/9639-headaches" target="_blank"> Know more...</a>
</p>
